6 6. That no bid may be read or considered if the bid does not fully comply with the
7 requirements of this section and that any deficient bid submitted must be resealed and
8 returned to the bidder immediately.
9 7. That the governing body reserves the right to reject any and all bids and rebid the
10 project until a satisfactory bid is received.
